prompt_text: Describe the scene of an airport.
content_text: I like going to the airport, so like to travel. I like to meet new people, get to know new places, new cultures. Oh, I love flying at night. It's more calm, less people rushing. Get there in the city in the morning and start the day from there. I don't like the airplane food, it's not very tasty. I like come. To travel, specially in my country, Mexico City, Cancun is my favorite spot to go.
